summary: I wonder if the reason why  Jon was READY to defend Daenerys was not because he loved her, but  because during the weeks they...
body:
I wonder if the reason why Jon was READY to defend Daenerys was not because he loved her, but because during the weeks they traveled to Winterfell..she told him her whole entire journey and what she has done to get to where she is now?

And why ‘whole journey’ I’m talking about Dany wanting to go back to the house with the red door and the lemon tree throwback. That just makes their love run more deep then I realise x
